      <mj-section mj-class="preSection">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text mj-class="p">Sorry for the lack of tips, I've spent the last few days cleansing my soul up in the Scottish Highlands. If you're enjoying the tips following on <a class="underA" href="https://twitter.com/GoodMarketingHQ" target="_blank">twitter</a> and forwarding to friends is appreciated.</mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="p">Cheers, <br>Harry</mj-text>
